ate my art as a tool of the sky.  </p>\n<p>After visiting Jodo-in, I walked towards Shaka-do and Ganzan-daishi-do.  </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ce14a44a7e3b463f1c5b19ed8c43dd42/72e01/shakado.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/ce14a44a7e3b463f1c5b19ed8c43dd42/8ac56/shakado.webp 240w,\n/static/ce14a44a7e3b463f1c5b19ed8c43dd42/d3be9/shakado.webp 480w,\n/static/ce14a44a7e3b463f1c5b19ed8c43dd42/e46b2/shakado.webp 960w,\n/static/ce14a44a7e3b463f1c5b19ed8c43dd42/a9a89/shakado.webp 1024w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/ce14a44a7e3b463f1c5b19ed8c43dd42/09b79/shakado.jpg 240w,\n/static/ce14a44a7e3b463f1c5b19ed8c43dd42/7cc5e/shakado.jpg 480w,\n/static/ce14a44a7e3b463f1c5b19ed8c43dd42/6a068/shakado.jpg 960w,\n/static/ce14a44a7e3b463f1c5b19ed8c43dd42/72e01/shakado.jpg 1024w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/ce14a44a7e3b463f1c5b19ed8c43dd42/6a068/shakado.jpg\"\n          alt=\"Shaka-do\"\n          title=\"Shaka-do\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>  </p>\n<p>This is Shaka-do.  </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-